{"tid":556594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得巴士有吐露港公路唔行，要行大埔公路山路係要照顧班圍村撚","createTime":"2018-02-10T14:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T23:48:57.000Z","uid":45148,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1670cd0120ade0d99ce41535f1af39dbd55046","tid":556594,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"單層就話算<br />\n雙層仲要行山路<br />\n又曲又彎<br />\n<br />\n明明有吐露港大路唔行<br />\n係要行小路大埔公路<br />\n<br />\n就係照顧班圍村撚<br />\n班圍村撚好心有錢住村屋就買車啦<br />\n搭咩公共交通工具<br />\n<br />\n成車人就因為照顧你地<br />\n巴士就要行小路<br />\n<br />\n無錢既搭小巴 又話者申請公屋<br />\n賣左你間野 買其他樓<br />\n<br />\n所以圍村撚都係自私撚"},{"pid":"d7919d290490d69ba67720036ef29f1bd1c3359d","tid":556594,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"你up 咩鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大埔公路好多私家樓喎<br />\n仲有中大落車個班人"},{"pid":"b3a0ee1654036778ad94eab6718533b5a6012dbc","tid":556594,"uid":145330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T23:10:17.000Z","msg":"樓主肯定無試過吐路港公路勁塞之後轉行舊路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋樓主肯定唔係大埔人 舊路不知幾多豪宅"},{"pid":"0afae1e95c3cf8ceb08aa1d2f945e4bf29ccf85b","tid":556594,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"大埔公路有赤泥坪又有九肚山<br />\n<br />\n樓豬知d唔知d"},{"pid":"83f497591792d4796f6f19f8ad0b5aed6d45816a","tid":556594,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T23:48:57.000Z","msg":"大埔公路沿路搵間圍村都難喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}